            "stanza_text": "Quelle colère injuste et folle !\n(Au fond la colère est injuste\nEt folle), mais combien frivole\nCette rancune si robuste !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Car robuste, elle l'est, hélas !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Jusqu'à me faire du chagrin,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Ta rancune, et je suis si las",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "De t'avoir paru ce matin",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Car robuste, elle l'est, hélas !\nJusqu'à me faire du chagrin,\nTa rancune, et je suis si las\nDe t'avoir paru ce matin"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Que ballottent quatre yeux de femmes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Comme autant d'astres de désastre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Qu'enfin sans néanmoins d'infâmes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Capitulations, à l'astre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Que ballottent quatre yeux de femmes,\nComme autant d'astres de désastre,\nQu'enfin sans néanmoins d'infâmes\nCapitulations, à l'astre"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Qu'est la bonté, qu'est la beauté",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "De ton âme et ton cœur si bons",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Et beaux comme la liberté,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Ô pardon ! Mais ô donc, réponds !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Qu'est la bonté, qu'est la beauté\nDe ton âme et ton cœur si bons\nEt beaux comme la liberté,\nÔ pardon ! Mais ô donc, réponds !"
        }
    ],
